{"type": "article", "id": 15318, "title": "防水压缩袋", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-23T06:50:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003385XKGkVZu2Lwatqjy.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t许多号称防水的背包并不能真正防水，外出旅行还是需要一个专业的防水压缩袋，放置换洗衣服或重要物品。比如旅行品牌 Travelon 的这款压缩袋，是采用 PVC 材料，能避免水分渗入。使用时拉紧压缩带，就能将空气排除，侧面的透明窗口也方便查看。必要的时候还可以当水上浮标。共有三种型号可选，分别可容纳 13L、8L和 5L。<a href=\"http://www.travelonbags.com/self-seal-dry-bag-medium\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142528jBpgveHnuVZPAiIq.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"452\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.41851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142529iMWtDCo4TyS6LGdj.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142529dBTP5WEN3zhRMw64.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}